cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on deep learning techniques for video analysis, specifically using 3D convolutional networks for spatiotemporal feature learning. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The paper also discusses the use of supervised learning and linear classifiers, which are common topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the benchmarks used in the paper are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
